name: Green Soporiferous  Seed
description:
Stare into the center of the circle! watch the whole video then close your eyes, what do you see? 

The Star Seed has formed outside of it's self growing too fast, I am unable to contain this breed, what have I done. I must stop it, but it's just so beautiful, no I can't, stop! the Seed is controlling me, must destroy it....
